2^n\cdot n! ≤ (n+1)^n
2^n\cdot n! ≤ 1+n^2
1+n^2 ≤ (n+1)^n
2^n ≤ n!
n = 1
2 \leq 2
n\geq 1
  2^{n+1}\cdot(n+1)! = 2(n+1)\cdot 2^n\cdot n! \operatorname*{\leq}_{\rm(IH)} 2(n+1)\cdot(n+1)^n = 2(n+1)^{n+1} 
 2\leq \left(\frac{n+2}{n+1}\right)^{n+1} = \left(1+\frac{1}{n+1}\right)^{n+1} (\operatorname*{\sim}_{n\to\infty} e) 
2(n+1)^{n+1}\leq\sum_{k=0}^{n+1} \binom {n+1}k(n+1)^{n-k+1}= (n+2)^{n+1} .
